result.title: Anyone willing to simulate contests in the GYM?
result.content:
Hello!

I am looking for one or two persons who want to make a team for the gym. I want to simulate a contest while we speak on G+ or Skype at the same time, because I want to experience team-working in a contest, I want to practice my English in this domain and, of course, I want to learn more about algorithms.

Your rating doesn't matter, but it would be a good matching if your rating is at least 1750. If you are interested about my proposal, please send me a message.
